room_title: Escape room "Contagion" by Gone in 60 Escape Games in Peoria
review: We were in a party of 7 and we got out with 3:48 left to spare. We had a great time and will definitely be coming back to do other rooms.

room_title: Escape room "Contagion" by Gone in 60 Escape Games in Peoria
review: Did the contagion room... it was fantastic and fun!

room_title: Escape room "Contagion" by Gone in 60 Escape Games in Peoria
review: We were part of a group of four. The room was very challenging and entertaining. It took all four of us to conquer The Contagion, going down to the wire. Highly recommended!

room_title: Escape room "Contagion" by Gone in 60 Escape Games in Peoria
review: The Contagion was so much fun!!!! We made it out with 5 minutes left. The room was very authentic and incredible detailed. I can't wait to go do Coven and the new rooms that are on their way.

room_title: Escape room "Contagion" by Gone in 60 Escape Games in Peoria
review: Conquered the Contagion room and had a blast solving the puzzles! Great time had by all. We even booked the Coven room before we left! Thanks Gone in 60 for a great time!

room_title: Escape room "Contagion" by Gone in 60 Escape Games in Peoria
review: Just did the Contagion room this evening. The theme was great and was a very challenging game! Wonderful people as well! We booked the Coven room for 2 weeks from now at the end. Highly recommended! Thanks to Gone in 60 for a great time!
